name: Nazeebo
title: Heretic Witch Doctor
description: Specialist Rule breakers and masters of unconventional warfare.

role.name: Specialist
role.description: Specialist Rule breakers and masters of unconventional warfare.

abilities.name: Corpse Spiders
abilities.description: Hurl a jar of spiders that deals 50 damage. If it hits at least one enemy, create 3 Corpse Spiders that attack for 38 damage. Spiders last for 4 seconds.

abilities.name: Zombie Wall
abilities.description: After 1 second, create a ring of Zombies surrounding the target area that deal 28 damage and last for 3 seconds.

abilities.name: Plague of Toads
abilities.description: Create a wave of 3 Toads that explode on contact, dealing 126 damage over 6 seconds. This effect stacks. Stores up to 2 charges.

heroics.name: Gargantuan
heroics.description: Summon a Gargantuan to guard an area for 20 seconds. Deals 100 damage when summoned, attacks for 150 damage, and can be ordered to stomp nearby enemies.

heroics.name: Ravenous Spirit
heroics.description: Channel a Ravenous Spirit that deals 216 damage per second. Cannot move while channeling. Lasts for 8 seconds.

original.name: Nazeebo
original.title: Heretic Witch Doctor
original.description: With cabalistic incantations and vestments of feather and bone, the witch doctor Nazeebo calls upon spirits from the Unformed Land to aid him. Few outlanders encounter a witch doctor in the flesh, without losing their own.
original.shortDescription: A sustained damage Mage who gains power when killing enemy minions.

trait.name: Voodoo Ritual
trait.description: Nazeebo's Basic Attacks and Abilities poison Non-Heroic enemies, causing them to take 67 additional damage over 6 seconds. Quest: If a Minion dies while poisoned by Voodoo Ritual, Nazeebo permanently gains 6 Health and 1 Mana.

skins.name: Heretic Witch Doctor
skins.description: With cabalistic incantations and vestments of feather and bone, the witch doctor Nazeebo calls upon spirits from the Unformed Land to aid him. Few outlanders encounter a witch doctor in the flesh, without losing their own.

skins.name: Hellflame Nazeebo
skins.description: The Hellflame Mask was created in honor of Nazeebo's victory over the Prime Evil. Trusting no one else to guard the black soulstone, he kept it close... Perhaps, too close.

skins.name: Gingerdread Nazeebo
skins.description: Run, run, run... as fast as you can! No one escapes from the Gingerdread Man.

skins.name: Harlequin Nazeebo
skins.description: The Countess Kerrigan's demands for entertainment mirror the darkness within her. Her harlequins are masters at manipulating life and death, solely for her amusement.

skins.name: Grimskull Nazeebo
skins.description: The Teganze jungles hold many legendary weapons wielded by both man and demon alike. The Grimskull Visage itself has passed from one Witch Doctor to the next since the Sin War.
